query:
SELECT 
                ta.id as "attempt_id!: Uuid",
                ta.task_id as "task_id!: Uuid",
                ta.pr_number as "pr_number!: i64",
                ta.pr_url as "pr_url!: String"
               FROM task_attempts ta
               WHERE ta.pr_status = 'open' AND ta.pr_number IS NOT NULL
